<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="egomotion.sitecontent">
<body>

<metal:main fill-slot="main">
  <metal:content-core define-macro="main">

  <article id="survey-view"
    tal:define="context_url context/absolute_url;
                has_token view/locked">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 tal:content="context/Title">Title inserted here</h1>
    </header>
    <section tal:condition="not:view/anonymous" class="alert alert-warning">
      <h4>Administration</h4>
      <p>Sie sind als Redakteur angemeldet:
        <a href="" tal:attributes="href python:context_url + '/@@survey-results'">
          <i class="icon-cog"></i>
          Umfrage Verwaltung</a>
      </p>
      <p>Um eine erneute Duchf√ºhrung der Umfrage ohne bereits zwischengespeicherter
        Daten zu beginnen, kann eine aktive Sitzung aus dem Zwischenspeicher
        entfernt werden:
        <a href="" tal:attributes="href python:context_url + '/@@survey-session-clear'">
          <i class="icon-refresh"></i>
          Sitzung bereinigen</a>
      </p>
      <p class="discreet"><i class="icon-info-sign"></i>
        IP: <span tal:content="view/get_client_ip" />
      </p>
    </section>

    <section tal:condition="has_token">
      <div class="alert alert-error">
        <h4 i18n:translate="">Hinweis</h4>
        <p i18n:translate="">
          Eine Teilnahme an unserer Umfrage ist nicht m&ouml;glich.
          Du hast bereits an unserer Umfrage teilgenommen.</p>
      </div>
      <h4 i18n:translate="">Weitere Informationen</h4>
      <p i18n:translate="">
        F&uuml;r Deinen Arbeitplatz wurde bereits eine abgeschlossene Teilnahme
        an unserer Umfrage gespeichert. Falls Du nicht selbst an unserer Umfrage
        teilgenommen hast, k&ouml;nnte es sein, dass bereits
        einmal aus Deinem Netzwerk alle Fragen beantwortet und abgeschickt wurden
        (z.B. durch einen Kollegen in Deinem B&uuml;ro).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section tal:condition="not:has_token">
      <h4 i18n:translate="">
        1. The following 15 design sketches show what RUFUS could look like as a
        product. Please choose three favourites from these sketches and state 
        which design features you like most and which features you like least.
      </h4>
      <div id="design-gallery"
        tal:condition="view/has_images">
        <tal:block tal:repeat="row view/image_matrix">
          <div class="gallery-row">
            <div class="pull-left" tal:repeat="cell row">
              <div class="design-thumbnail" tal:define="item cell/item">
                <a href=""
                  data-appui="gallery"
                  class="prettyPhoto[design-gallery]"
                  rel="prettyPhoto[design-gallery]"
                  tal:attributes="href item/original_url">
                  <img class="img-polaroid"
                    tal:attributes="src python:item['thumb_url'];
                                    width item/thumb_width;
                                    height item/thumb_height;
                                    data-image-url item/original_url;
                                    data-image-width item/original_width;
                                    data-image-height item/original_height" />
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </tal:block>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="visualClear"
      tal:condition="not:has_token">
      <form id="form-survey" method="post"
        data-appui="autosave"
        tal:define="context_url context/absolute_url"
        tal:attributes="action request/URL;
                        data-appui-target python:context_url + '/@@autosave-survey'">

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">My favourites</h4>
          <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite1 | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1"
                  i18n:translate="">Number</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-mini"
                    id="favorite1"
                    name="favorite1"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                    <div class="help-block error"
                      tal:condition="err_msg">
                      <i class="icon-warning-sign" />
                      <span tal:replace="python:error['msg']" />
                    </div>
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 1 -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite1.likes | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.likes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like most</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.likes.one"
                    name="favorite1.likes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.likes.two"
                    name="favorite1.likes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.likes.three"
                    name="favorite1.likes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite1 like -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite1.dislikes.one | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.dislikes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like least</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.dislikes.one"
                    name="favorite1.dislikes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.dislikes.two"
                    name="favorite1.dislikes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite1.dislikes.three"
                    name="favorite1.dislikes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 1 dislike -->
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite2 | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1"
                  i18n:translate="">Number</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-mini"
                    id="favorite2"
                    name="favorite2"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                    <div class="help-block error"
                      tal:condition="err_msg">
                      <i class="icon-warning-sign" />
                      <span tal:replace="python:error['msg']" />
                    </div>
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 2 -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite2.likes | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.likes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like most</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.likes.one"
                    name="favorite2.likes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.likes.two"
                    name="favorite2.likes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.likes.three"
                    name="favorite2.likes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 2 like -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite2.dislikes.one | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.dislikes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like least</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.dislikes.one"
                    name="favorite2.dislikes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.dislikes.two"
                    name="favorite2.dislikes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite2.dislikes.three"
                    name="favorite2.dislikes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 2 dislike -->
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite3 | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1"
                  i18n:translate="">Number</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-mini"
                    id="favorite3"
                    name="favorite3"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                    <div class="help-block error"
                      tal:condition="err_msg">
                      <i class="icon-warning-sign" />
                      <span tal:replace="python:error['msg']" />
                    </div>
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 1 -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite3.likes | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.likes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like most</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.likes.one"
                    name="favorite3.likes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.likes.two"
                    name="favorite3.likes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.likes.three"
                    name="favorite3.likes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite1 like -->
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
              <div class="control-group field"
                tal:define="error errors/favorite1.dislikes.one | nothing;
                            err_msg python:error and error['active'] == True"
                tal:attributes="class python:err_msg and 'control-group error' or 'control-group'">
                <label class="control-label"
                  for="favorite1.dislikes.one"
                  i18n:translate="">Features which I like least</label>
                <div class="controls">
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.dislikes.one"
                    name="favorite3.dislikes.one"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.dislikes.two"
                    name="favorite3.dislikes.two"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    class="input-xlarge"
                    id="favorite3.dislikes.three"
                    name="favorite3.dislikes.three"
                    tal:attributes="value python:error and view.default_value(error) or ''" />
                </div>
              </div><!-- / favorite 1 dislike -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            2. What do you like least about the other sketches?
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <div class="controls">
              <div class="input-prepend">
                <span class="add-on discreet">a.</span>
                <input class="input-xxlarge" id="dislikes.one"
                  name="dislikes.one"
                  type="text"
                  tal:attributes="value python:view.default_value(fieldname='dislikes.one')">
              </div>
              <div class="input-prepend">
                <span class="add-on discreet">b.</span>
                <input class="input-xxlarge" id="dislikes.two"
                  name="dislikes.two"
                  type="text"
                  tal:attributes="value python:view.default_value(fieldname='dislikes.two')">
              </div>
              <div class="input-prepend">
                <span class="add-on discreet">c.</span>
                <input class="input-xxlarge" id="dislikes.three"
                  name="dislikes.three"
                  type="text"
                  tal:attributes="value python:view.default_value(fieldname='dislikes.three')">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div><!-- / favorites global dislike -->
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            3. Which other functions should the running coach have in addition
            to those mentioned above in your opinion?
          </h4>

          <div class="help-block" i18n:translate="">
            (You can select more than one answer here)
          </div>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.1" name="functionality"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='functionality')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A program for monitoring performance (e.g. a program which
                  analyses my pulse as the strain on your body changes,
                  like in a exercise ECG)
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.2" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A function which allows me to record and analyse my running
                  behaviour later on in the form of a training transcript
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.3" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A function which offers me strength and flexibility training
                  as part of my running training
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.4" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A function which includes my mood in the design of my training sessions
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.5" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A function which suggests a diet based on my calorie consumption
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.6" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A navigation programme for running unfamiliar routes
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="functionality.7" name="functionality">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  A function which allows me to organise a virtual running meeting
                  with my friends (e.g. a video conference via Skype with friends
                  who are too far away for me to meet with in person) 
                </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">Other</span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="functionality.additional"
                name="functionality.additional"
                type="text" placeholder="Type additional information here if you wish"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder"
                >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon functionality -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4><span i18n:translate="">
            4. Which accessories should the running coach have in your opinion?</span><br />
            <small i18n:translate="">(You can select more than one answer here)</small>
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="accessory.1" name="accessory"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='accessory.one')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Lights, bell, lock
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="accessory.2" name="accessory"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='accessory.two')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Bottle holder, storage compartment (&quot;glove compartment&quot;)
                  for keys and other small items
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="accessory.3" name="accessory"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='accessory.three')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Media fixtures and connection points (smartphone docking station, USB port, etc.)
                </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">Other</span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="accessory.additional"
                name="accessory.additional"
                type="text" placeholder="Type additional information here if you wish"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder"
                tal:attributes="value python:view.default_value(fieldname='accessory.additional')">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4><span i18n:translate="">
            5. Which additional benefits should the running coach have in your opinion?
            </span><br />
            <small i18n:translate="">(You can select more than one answer here)</small>
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="benefit.1" name="benefit"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='benefit.one')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  I would like to be able to use it to go jogging when I do my shopping (fixings for a shopping basket).
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="benefit.2" name="benefit"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='benefit.two')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  I would like to be able to go jogging with my children (fixings for a child or baby seat).
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="benefit.3" name="benefit"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='benefit.three')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  I would like to be able to transport heavy loads with it as
                  well and ride it myself.
                </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">Other</span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="benefit.additional"
                type="text" placeholder="Type additional information here if you wish"
                name="benefit.additional"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder"
                tal:attributes="value python:view.default_value(fieldname='benefit.additional')">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            6. How often do you go running?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="frequency" id="frequency1" value="frequency.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Regularly (several times a week)
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="frequency" id="frequency2" value="frequency.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Frequently (not every week but several times a month)
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="frequency" id="frequency3" value="frequency.3">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Occasionally
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="frequency" id="frequency4" value="frequency.4">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Never, but I've been thinking about taking up running for a long time
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="frequency" id="frequency5" value="frequency.5">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Never. I don't like running.
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="alert">
            <p><i class="icon-info-sign"></i>
            <span i18n:translate="">
              If you've answered this question with
              &quot;Never. I don't like running.&quot;, go straight to question 13.
            </span>
            </p>
            <p>
            <a href="#survey-question-13"
              data-appui="pagescroll" data-target="#survey-question-13"
               i18n:translate="">
              Jump to question 13
            </a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
          </p>
        </div>


        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            7. How important is systematic running training (based on a training
            plan, for example) to you?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="roadwork" id="roadwork1" value="roadwork.1"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='roadwork')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Very important
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="roadwork" id="roadwork2" value="roadwork.2"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='roadwork')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Important
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="roadwork" id="roadwork3" value="roadwork.3"
                tal:attributes="checked python:view.default_value(fieldname='roadwork')">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Unimportant
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4>
            <span i18n:translate="">
              8. Which aids do you use for your running training?
            </span><br />
            <small i18n:translate="">(You can select more than one answer here)</small>
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.1" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Heart rate monitor without GPS
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.2" name="trainingresource"
                 i18n:translate="">
                Heart rate monitor with GPS
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.3" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Treadmill at home
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.4" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Treadmill at the gym
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.5" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Personal running coach at a club
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.6" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Private personal running coach
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.7" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Running group at a club
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.8" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Private running group
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.9" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Training app on my smartphone
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="trainingresource.10" name="trainingresource">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Pedometer with calorie consumption
                </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">Other</span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="trainingresource.additional"
                name="trainingresource.additional"
                type="text" placeholder="Type additional information here if you wish"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            9. How effectively do these aids support you when training? In
            particular, how well do they help you monitor your heart rate and
            running speed?
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="trainingresource.effect"
                value="trainingresource.effect.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Excellently. I'm making very good training progress (endurance and speed)
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="trainingresource.effect"
                value="trainingresource.effect.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Adequately, but I could be making better training progress.
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="trainingresource.effect"
                value="trainingresource.effect.3">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Poorly. I'm hardly making any training progress.
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            10. Assuming you train with a heart rate monitor, how accurately are
            you able to control your heart rate and running speed with this
            heart rate monitor (with a pedometer or GPS)?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.monitor" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.monitor.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Well</span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.monitor" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.monitor.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Ok</span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.monitor" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.monitor.3">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Poorly</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            11. How important is it to you to have a personal running coach
            which is available to you at any time and completes a training
            programme specifically tailored to suit you with you?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.personalization" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.personalization.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Very important
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.personalization" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.personalization.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Important
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.personalization" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.personalization.3">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Unimportant
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            12. What is the maximum you would be prepared to pay for such a
            running coach per training hour?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.maxprice" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.maxprice.1">
              25 - 50 EUR
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.maxprice" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.maxprice.2">
              50 - 75 EUR
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="training.maxprice" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="training.maxprice.3">
              75 - 100 EUR
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question" id="survey-question-13">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            13. Age and sex
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <div class="input-append">
              <input class="span1" id="appendedInput" type="text"
                name="participant.age">
              <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">years old</span>
            </div>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.gender" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="participant.gender.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Female
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio inline">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.gender" id="optionsRadios1"
                value="participant.gender.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Male
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            14. Professional position
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios1"
                value="participant.occupation.1">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Pupil/student
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios2"
                value="participant.occupation.2">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Unemployed person
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios3"
                value="participant.occupation.3">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Blue-collar/clerical worker
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios4"
                value="participant.occupation.4">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Employee with responsibility for other employees / civil servant in the middle grade of the civil service
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios5"
                value="participant.occupation.5">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Executive / civil servant in the upper grade of the civil service
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios6"
                value="participant.occupation.6">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Managing director / board member
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios7"
                value="participant.occupation.7">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Self-employed person / freelancer
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios8"
                value="participant.occupation.8">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Entrepreneur
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios9"
                value="participant.occupation.9">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Pensioner
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="radio">
              <input type="radio" name="participant.occupation" id="participantOccupationRadios10"
                value="participant.occupation.10">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Other
                </span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            15. Approximately how much have you invested sport and wellness in
            the last year?
          </h4>
          <div class="controls">
            <div class="input-append">
              <input class="span1" id="appendedInput"
                name="investment"
                type="text">
              <span class="add-on discreet">EUR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4><span i18n:translate="">
            16. What did you spend this money on?
            </span><br />
            <small i18n:translate="">(You can select more than one answer here)</small>
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="participant.investment.1" name="participant.investment">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Sports equipment
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="participant.investment.2" name="participant.investment">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Coach sessions
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="participant.investment.3" name="participant.investment">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Sports clothing
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="participant.investment.4" name="participant.investment">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Wellness (saunas, massages)
                </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="participant.investment.5" name="participant.investment">
                <span i18n:translate="">
                  Gym fees
                </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">Other</span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="participant.investment.additional"
                type="text" placeholder="Type additional information here if you wish"
                name="participant.investment.additional"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            17. Approximately how much would you spend on the products listed
            below?
          </h4>

          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label" for="inputWarning"
               i18n:translate="">
              A home exercise machine
            </label>
            <div class="controls">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.hometrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.hometrainer.1">
                100 &ndash; 250 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.hometrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.hometrainer.2">
                250 &ndash; 500 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.hometrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.hometrainer.3">
                500 &ndash; 1500 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label" for="inputWarning"
               i18n:translate="">
              A treadmill
            </label>
            <div class="controls">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.treadmill" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.treadmill.1">
                500 &ndash; 1000 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.treadmill" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.treadmill.2">
                1000 &ndash; 2000 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.treadmill" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.treadmill.3">
                2000 &ndash; 3000 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label" for="inputWarning"
               i18n:translate="">
              A cross trainer
            </label>
            <div class="controls">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.crosstrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.crosstrainer.1">
                500 &ndash; 1000 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.crosstrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.crosstrainer.2">
                1000 &ndash; 2000 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.crosstrainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.crosstrainer.3">
                2000 &ndash; 3000 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group visualClear">
            <label class="control-label"
               i18n:translate="">
              A racing bike
            </label>
            <div class="controls">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.bike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.bike.1">
                300 &ndash; 1000 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.bike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.bike.2">
                1000 &ndash; 2500 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.bike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.bike.3">
                2500 &ndash; 7500 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group visualClear">
            <label class="control-label"
               i18n:translate="">
              A mountain bike
            </label>
            <div class="controls">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.mountainbike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.mountainbike.1">
                150&ndash; 750 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.mountainbike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.mountainbike.2">
                750 &ndash; 1500 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.mountainbike" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.mountainbike.3">
                1500 &ndash; 3000 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group visualClear">
            <label class="control-label" i18n:translate="">
              A coach session
            </label>
            <div class="controls controls-row">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.trainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.trainer.1">
                25 &ndash; 50 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.trainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.trainer.2">
                50 &ndash; 75 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.trainer" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.trainer.3">
                75 &ndash; 100 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control-group visualClear">
            <label class="control-label" i18n:translate="">
              Monthly subscription for a fitness club
            </label>
            <div class="controls controls-row">
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.club" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.club.1">
                20 &ndash; 50 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.club" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.club.2">
                50 &ndash; 80 EUR
              </label>
              <label class="radio inline">
                <input type="radio" name="price.club" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="price.club.3">
                80 &ndash; 120 EUR
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- / addon products -->

        <div class="survey-question">
          <h4 i18n:translate="">
            18. RUFUS will cost about 2000 EUR (cost of a good racing bike or
            treadmill) when it enters the market. Would you buy yourself a
            RUFUS?
          </h4>
          <div class="control-group visualClear">
            <label class="control-label" i18n:translate="">
              Monatsabo im Fitnessclub
            </label>
            <div class="controls controls-row">
              <label class="radio">
                <input type="radio" name="purchase" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="purchase.1">
                  <span i18n:translate="">
                    Yes, if the design, functionality, and quality are right for me.
                  </span>
              </label>
              <label class="radio">
                <input type="radio" name="purchase" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="purchase.2">
                  <span i18n:translate="">
                  No</span>
              </label>
              <label class="radio">
                <input type="radio" name="purchase" id="optionsRadios1"
                  value="purchase.3">
                  <span i18n:translate="">
                    Don't know yet
                  </span>
              </label>
            </div>
          <div id="nopurchase" class="controls">
              <label for="purchase.comment" i18n:translate="">
                Reasons
              </label>
              <textarea rows="3" class="input-xxlarge"
                id="purchase.comment" name="purchase.comment">
              </textarea>
              <span class="help-block" i18n:translate="">
                If your answer is &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Don't know yet&quot;, it would be very
                helpful if you could provide with a short explanation for
                your answer.
              </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="survey-question">
          <div class="controls">
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="interest.1" name="interest">
              <span i18n:translate="">
                Yes, I am interested in RUFUS and would like to be updated on
                its progress and when it is to enter the market.
              </span>
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" value="interest.2" name="interest">
                <span  i18n:translate="">
                I think RUFUS is a great product idea and would like to make
                use of a non-binding purchase option which will give me a
                early-bird discount of 25%. I understand that I can relinquish
                this option at any time without providing further notification.
              </span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-prepend">
               <span class="add-on discreet" i18n:translate="">
                Email address
               </span>
              <input class="input-xxlarge" id="email" type="text"
                name="email"
                placeholder="john@example.tld"
                i18n:attributes="placeholder">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <span tal:replace="structure context/@@authenticator/authenticator" />
        <!-- Form actions -->
        <div class="xform-actions" id="survey-form-actions">
          <input type="submit"
            class="btn btn-primary btn-large pull-right"
            id="btn-submit"
            name="form.buttons.Submit"
            value="Submit questionnaire"
            i18n:attributes="value" />
        </div>
      </form>
    </section>
  </article>
  </metal:content-core>
</metal:main>

</body>
</html>

